NAME
	exploration

SYNOPSYS
	exploration
	exploration guess <number>

DESCRIPTION
	The exploration command will display the number of rooms you have
	visited, and the number of items (weapons, armours, food, herbs,
	drinks, potions, torches and containers) and beings (persons,
	monsters or animals) you have noticed using the "notice" command.

OPTIONS
	<number> - your guess for the total number of rooms in the realms.

SEE ALSO
	notice
